document.full_text: rory mcilroy, who led through three rounds of the masters before a disastrous final round last sunday, birdied his final hole to take a two-stroke lead at the malaysian open in kuala lumpur.
document.title: sports briefing | golf: mcilroy rebounds to lead a rainy malaysian open
